track_notes: Route goes via access land over the Wainwright Outlyer of Flat Fell (LDO-082). The access land is left to reach Dent. Then steeply downhill to Nannycatch Gate on Wainwrights Coast to Coast route.

Follow the forest road to the ridge, then branch off along the ridge. This route takes you to a very small cairn on the summit. The larger cairns to the west are in the Activation Zone but slightly lower. They do have a better view and I suspect most activations take place from there.
This route brings you to the main cairn first, this is not the true summit but has the better views to the local area. The true summit is a small cairn. This route is also the Coast to Coast route.
track_title: A direct route from Black How
